.TH NVRUN "1" "July 2026" "nvrun version 1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
nvrun \- manual page for nvrun version 1.0
.SH DESCRIPTION
usage: nvrun [\-h] [\-s] [\-v]
.PP
NVIDIA Prime Offload Launcher & Power Status Utility. Without arguments, nvrun
will display this help menu. Provide an executable command to run it using the
discrete NVIDIA GPU.
.SS "options:"
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
show this help message and exit
.TP
\fB\-s\fR, \fB\-\-status\fR
Print the current hardware power state of the NVIDIA GPU
(e.g., D3cold, D0).
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version info and exit.
